Hi! Can you say, inviting trouble? Fair is fair. Trying to place limits on the larger guilds, which you already said could control the Ragefire camp/list if they wanted, would have the potential of pushing them to that point. Tell a large, capable guild who could port in and take Rage at any time, that they can't get a cleric on the list, and what ya think will happen? Eventually, someone is gonna get fed up.<br>
<br>
The list is a good idea, it just needs some work I think. Make it fair for everyone, or it won't last. Try to shut out anyone, and the people you shut out will end up shoving the list down someone's throat.<br>
